2012年6月20日，Rihanna  在Nicky Romero 和 Burns 的协作下，开始第七张专辑的录制工作。<ref>{{cite web|author=Published Wednesday, Jun 20 2012, 11:55 BST |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a388515/rihanna-recording-new-material-during-trip-to-london.html |title=Rihanna recording new music during trip to London – Music News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2012-06-20 |accessdate=2012-09-21}}</ref> Rihanna 和 Burns 预订了伦敦一间录音室三天的使用时间。与此同时，Rihanna 进行了 [[Radio_1's_Big_Weekend|Radio 1's Hackney Weekend]] 上的表演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gigwise.com/news/74879/rihannas-next-producer-burns-reveals-new-single-lies |title=Rihanna's next producer Burns reveals new single 'Lies' |publisher=Gigwise |date=2012-07-25 |accessdate=2012-09-21}}</ref>Eric Bellinger, [[Sean_Garrett|Sean Garrett]] 和 [[Swedish_House_Mafia|Swedish House Mafia]] 被证实也在和 Rihanna 一起准备第七张专辑。<ref>{{cite web|author=Becky Bain |url=http://idolator.com/6640792/rihanna-refuses-to-take-a-break-begins-work-on-seventh-album#more-6640792 |title=Rihanna Refuses To Take A Break, Begins Work On Seventh Album | Music News, Reviews, and Gossip on |publisher=Idolator.com |date= |accessdate=2012-09-29}}</ref> 2012年7月6日， [[Def_Jam|Def Jam]] 的执行 [[No_I.D.|No I.D.]] 透露他在与 Rihanna 一起准备新专辑，“I’m going in next week for about a week”.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2012/07/06/rap-up-tv-no-id-talks-nas-kanye-west-and-rihanna-albums/ |title=Rap-Up TV: No I.D. Talks Nas, Kanye West, and Rihanna Albums |publisher=Rap-Up.com |date= |accessdate=2012-09-21}}</ref>2012年7月10日，英国唱作歌手[[Labrinth|Labrinth]] 向 Capital FM 透露他开始与 Rihanna 合作下一张专辑，"I'm supposed to be working with her soon hopefully so I've spoke to her managers, I think she's currently working on some stuff so everybody's in there at the moment and she's working in certain studios so it seems like it's very exciting. She's not in my studio [yet] but hopefully I'll have some hot ones on her album."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a392537/rihanna-to-work-with-labrinth-for-new-album.html |title=Rihanna to work with Labrinth for new album – Music News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2012-07-10 |accessdate=2012-09-29}}</ref>2012年7月17日，据报道 Rihanna 将与 R&B 歌手 [[Ne-Yo|Ne-Yo]] 和 [[N-Dubz|N-Dubz]] 的成员 [[Fazer_(rapper)|Fazer]] 合作. 在 Capital FM 对 Ne-Yo 的一次访问中，Ne-Yo 提到了与Rihanna 的合作， "I just recently went in to do some stuff for Rihanna, you know. She’s the hardest working woman in showbiz right now. She’s in the process of putting together a new album as we speak, I got in with [[Stargate_(production_team)|StarGate]] and [[David_Guetta|David Guetta]] and a few other people for that project.（我最近才开始为 Rihanna 做些事情，要知道，她现在是娱乐界工作最努力的女性。就像我们说的那样，她现在正在整合一张新专辑，我与 [[Stargate_(production_team)|StarGate]] 和 [[David_Guetta|David Guetta]]还有其他几个人正致力于此。）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://singersroom.com/content/2012-07-16/Rihanna-Drafts-Ne-Yo-and-Fazer-for-Seventh-Album-/ |title=News | Rihanna Drafts Ne-Yo and Fazer for Seventh Album? |publisher=Singersroom |date=2012-07-16 |accessdate=2012-09-29}}</ref>

2012年7月13日，[[Sean_Garrett|Sean Garrett]] 确认他正在和法国 DJ [[David_Guetta|David Guetta]] 为 Rihanna 的专辑在录音室忙着， "I was in the studio with David doing some stuff for Rihanna recently. He finds inspiration in the things I don't like, and I get excited by the things he doesn't like. He wants to be more urban and I want to be more international, so we push each other, I try to help Rihanna. She works hard and it's cool to write for someone who is so open-minded.（我最近正和 David 在录音室为 Rihanna 的东西忙碌着。他能在我不喜欢的东西上找到灵感，我在他讨厌的东西上找到兴奋点。他希望能更加都市化而我想更国际化，所以我们互相促进。我尝试着给 Rihanna 带来帮助。她工作确实努力，而给如此虚心的人写歌是非常酷的一件事情。）"<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/rihanna/360764-rihanna-david-guetta-sean-garrett-new-album |title=Rihanna Working With David Guetta On New Album | Rihanna | News | MTV UK |publisher=Mtv.co.uk |date=2012-07-30 |accessdate=2012-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214155820/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/rihanna/360764-rihanna-david-guetta-sean-garrett-new-album |archive-date=2013-12-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 2012年8月21日， 美国作词者 Claude Kelly 透露在 Rihanna 进行伦敦演出的同时他在为 Rihanna 写歌 ， "Rihanna's a worldwide superstar at this point and she's performing in stadiums and arenas now, so I wanted songs that reflected her audience, when I was in London she was performing at a festival in front of like 30,000 to 40,000 people. So I didn't want small songs that only worked on radio, so I tried to do anthemic big stadium-themed songs."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rihanna/news/new-album-stadium-songs/ |title=Rihanna's New Album Will Be Full Of "Anthemic Stadium Songs" |publisher=Capital FM |date=2012-08-21 |accessdate=2012-09-29}}</ref>
